Schubert (1986) erroneously considered all material from Møns Klint in eastern Denmark as late Maastrichtian. However, no sediments from the late Maastrichtian crop out at Møns Klint (cf.
Mutterlose et al. 1998
) and the samples studied by Schubert (1986) are in fact labelled as early Maastrichtian.
